# Switch to dvorak (Linux)

setxkbmap dvorak
gsettings set org.gnome.desktop.input-sources sources "[('xkb', 'us+dvorak')]"

# If running those doesn't work, try this;
sudo dpkg-reconfigure keyboard-configuration

# A LOT more information and tips about Dvorak can be found here;
# https://gitlab.com/snippets/1997412
# (^ recommended reading ^)